nodes.text: A cantina was owned by Fey Zara. She was assisted by the protocol droid B7-N5. It hosted a series of holotables upon which patrons could play games based on the pivotal conflicts of galactic history. Patrons included Shar, Doctor M'ak Nar, Adjunct Bam Teel, and Garudda the Hutt.
This cantina serves as the setting of the 2015 mobile game Star Wars: Galaxy of Heroes.
